column5: I wouldn't have just tossed it back for dinner if it was attacking my dog. It would have taken a few bashes to the head, or it's coming home with me for dinner! LOL
would not happen if that was real hunting dog in the boat.

if that was my shed dog in that boat that goose wouldnt have lasted the first round.  great vid, certainly made my day, especially since ive been attacked by geese on many many occasions.  cheers mike
I think I would have killed it, if that was me with my hands around it's neck

Wouldn't that be Bill Dance LOL  cause it sure sounded like him LOL  Talk about being protective..... must of been a little one close by to have this bird react like that I'd have this thing guard my house and not have to worry about a thing LOL  Thanks for sharing dnb_cbr.... crazy goose for sure!! Leechman
